Calls to <%= @number %> currently receive a pre-recorded message saying
"This phone number does not receive voice calls; please send a text message
instead".  <input type="submit" value="Use JMP without calls" />
</p>
</form>

<p>
Otherwise please choose one of the following options for receiving calls to your
JMP number (the selected number or SIP address will receive a call; enter the
verification code it provides to you on the next page):
</p>

